OL,4,G0100FOutback Truckers
OL,5,     GA driver travels through an area
OL,6,     Gwhere bush fire has run wild. An
OL,7,     Gowner operator faces the busiest
OL,8,     Gweek of his career.
OL,9,G0200FTrucking Hell
OL,10,     GWhen a driver transporting booze
OL,11,     Gdecouples at a lorry park, his
OL,12,     Gtrailer's landing legs are
OL,13,     Gswallowed by some porous tarmac.
OL,14,     GThe recovery pushes Jordan and
OL,15,     GMerrie's skills to the limit.
OL,16,G0305FTrucking Hell
OL,17,     GThere's an emergency in East
OL,18,     GLondon when a 25-ton truck hits a
OL,19,     Grailway bridge. And Buzz needs to
OL,20,     Gco-ordinate a multi-agency
OL,21,     Gtaskforce when a refrigerated
OL,22,     Glorry catches fire on the A42.
